_sText:
If you've played MW2, this may look familiar as I based it off of one of my favorite maps, Skidrow.  It's not meant to be exactly the same, but the basic layout is very similar. Battle through the streets or the hallways.  Two bombsites, one is at CT spawn, the other in the middle building.

Although this map is based on the MW2 map "Skidrow," I made it all from memory, did not look at the actual map at all for like a year.  Worked hard on this for 3 days to get accustomed to hammer again after a long break :D
